{"tid":1481603,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對抗FB/IG/YouTube五毛的最佳做法","createTime":"2019-08-17T18:35:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T20:10:07.000Z","uid":71237,"like":96,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"368ca0b5781e71c019f7e967a5fd788073825383","tid":1481603,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:35:25.000Z","msg":"見到好多連登仔都好緊張Facebook、IG被五毛洗版。<br />\n有好多post呼召巴打去FB逐個自己人的留言比like，甚至將五毛的留言逐個反駁。<br />\n如果你有親身做過，就會發現咁做其實係十分浪費時間，而且好似打極都打唔完。<br />\n<br />\n為了更好地運用你的時間，我有以下建議：<br />\n<br />\n1. 只要無人睇，五毛的留言並不可怕。<br />\n蘋果日報的FB page每日都出十幾廿個post，每個post都幾千個留言。<br />\n真係唔會有人睇哂所有留言，亦都唔會有太多人搵返舊post嚟睇。<br />\n因此五毛的言論都未必有人睇，唔值得你辛辛苦苦打千字文去反駁。<br />\n如果你有時間，不妨思考下點樣先發揮到最大效果。<br />\n例如落街搞連儂牆、幫手寫文宣、幫手建立反駁藍絲的資料庫、寫維基百科，好多嘢比Facebook罵戰更值得去做。<br />\n我下面有其他建議，你可以睇埋落去。<br />\n<br />\n2. 五毛留言都需要時間，再多的留言都鬥唔過del post<br />\n一個Facebook page的小編出一個post只需要幾分鐘的時間。<br />\n假設FB出一個post，會吸引到1000個五毛嚟留言洗版，而五毛每留言一次需要10秒。<br />\n即係話小編用少少時間出一個post，就可以消耗到對家10000秒。然後你只要delete個post，依1000個五毛留言就馬上灰飛煙滅。<br />\ndelete完post之後，小編又可以馬上再出返一模一樣的post。成個過程當中你只需要幾分鐘，就可以浪費到對家大量時間。<br />\n因此你應該開設Facebook / IG / YouTube account，不停大量張貼文宣，吸引五毛留言。<br />\n等留言累積到一定地步，就del post，然後再重新upload。咁做好過你不停喺comments同五毛鬧交。<br />\n<br />\n3. 搞多啲無謂投票、問卷浪費藍絲時間<br />\n其實你用Google Form、<a href=\"http://surveymonkey.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsurveymonkey.com&d=qWNbGjuqVnVY%2B89Bav9Y1L3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=0a4a6242\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">surveymonkey.com</a>好容易就可以整到一啲投票、問卷。<br />\n你可以搞多啲投票、問卷，最好要對方寫下自己的感想、寫幾句支持下香港警察，總之要消耗對方多啲時間。跟住諗辦法share去藍絲group，改啲吸引啲的標題，等佢地廣傳。<br />\n假設有幾萬個藍絲參與投票、填問卷，跟住你一嘢delete咗個投票，佢地投票的時間就等於白白浪費咗。"},{"pid":"7d42a8c2eb770171bee9c796c5f86d3b372009a9","tid":1481603,"uid":82829,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:37:49.000Z","msg":"3.<br />\n一個做問卷五分鐘<br />\n一千個人做你del咗就浪費五千分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76b9f79b3a2206d63e0fb8b88967e3b2d67f60a4","tid":1481603,"uid":71237,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:38:43.000Z","msg":"就算有一億個五毛去Facebook page留言我都唔驚，佢地多數只係集中喺最新果一兩個post留言。<br />\n只要聽日我出多幾個post洗走佢，或者直頭delete post，佢地啲留言就會唔見哂。根本唔洗花時間去駁，你不斷出post浪費佢地時間就得。<br />\n依招喺IG特別重要。"},{"pid":"101f886014c94be4b1abd8cf73880346e808ffd1","tid":1481603,"uid":225807,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:41:17.000Z","msg":"同佢鬥紅咪得 你紅呀 我仲紅過你 愛黨愛國<br />\n上次屌5毛屌到佢同我say返sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e21b445b6bc099407e8a2cab03c4954b45e8faca","tid":1481603,"uid":71237,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"7d42a8c2eb770171bee9c796c5f86d3b372009a9","tid":1481603,"uid":82829,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:37:49.000Z","msg":"3.<br />\n一個做問卷五分鐘<br />\n一千個人做你del咗就浪費五千分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:45:14.000Z","msg":"delete咗之後仲可以聲稱係比黃絲搞到delete咗，要求大家再填多次。"},{"pid":"5e4e6b2e6e8c59c079aa54a13c05774ad0ad799c","tid":1481603,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:50:47.000Z","msg":"聽日衝衝既勇武派 睇睇郭文貴呢段片先<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.guo.media/broadcasts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.guo.media%2Fbroadcasts&d=qWNbGjuqVnVY%2B89Bav9Y1L3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=2a2ea8f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.guo.media/broadcasts</a><br />\n2:00：00開始睇<br />\n千其咪衝<br />\n唔好掉入 香港700萬 對14 億既陷阱<br />\n中共想你地敵對<br />\n根本垃圾魔鬼黎<br />\n你地鬥完 就唔會燒到共產黨<br />\n狠毒到仆街既共狗黨"},{"pid":"6223fc7c35badab47ef39fb81e36af9ae11eaada","tid":1481603,"uid":71237,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:53:53.000Z","msg":"頭先喺連登見到有人擔心如果蘋果日報 / 立場新聞的top comments如果係五毛的comments，會令少咗人出去示威。<br />\n老老實實，睇開蘋果日報 / 立場新聞的自己人唔會因為一兩個五毛留言而轉軑。咁容易轉軑的本身都唔係自己人啦。<br />\n<br />\nlike咗蘋果日報 / 立場新聞的人，主要都係睇返小編出的post，comments的影響力其實好有限。"},{"pid":"1232aabee54978afb413cffff8133a1ed66be672","tid":1481603,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:58:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">make more efficient use of your time</span></span>"},{"pid":"db7b200acdea58e56c3892def2265b9ee45d61a9","tid":1481603,"uid":93383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T19:09:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d7aa85e46ce2940bca802d306a07ce0a80c2be4","tid":1481603,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T19:10:25.000Z","msg":"等我幫大家諗啲吸引藍絲的標題<br />\n大家唔洗100%跟足，可以base on我的建議再改良：<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f02f8013166def3656e2f1583ee8dcc6f5288bec","tid":1481603,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d7aa85e46ce2940bca802d306a07ce0a80c2be4","tid":1481603,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T19:10:25.000Z","msg":"等我幫大家諗啲吸引藍絲的標題<br />\n大家唔洗100%跟足，可以base on我的建議再改良：<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T19:13:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce443e002be0d10eb918d0f2c6b036d7326163ab","tid":1481603,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T19:22:12.000Z","msg":"要有效率咁消耗對方時間<br />\n你消耗到對方時間，佢地去第二度搞事嘅時間都會減少。"},{"pid":"460091ca377348807de2a91c8839b1475f5f8f4e","tid":1481603,"uid":71237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T19:25:45.000Z","msg":"同時我們自己都要小心避免跌入陷阱。<br />\n<br />\n好多人以為FB比嬲嬲或者YouTube比Dislike就可以令對家收皮<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/dudekT\" target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/dudekT</a>"},{"pid":"11235845ede3194156db51af23561cd3950b5e1c","tid":1481603,"uid":231071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T19:31:02.000Z","msg":"其實留咗言咪即係等於幫佢地賺多五毛?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3c3dce4e5ba1fa23044d6bb96a7794aa8f96955","tid":1481603,"uid":71237,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"11235845ede3194156db51af23561cd3950b5e1c","tid":1481603,"uid":231071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T19:31:02.000Z","msg":"其實留咗言咪即係等於幫佢地賺多五毛?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T19:41:51.000Z","msg":"有好多係真心藍絲。<br />\n<br />\n同樣藍絲去蘋果日報fb page留言, 比嬲嬲<br />\n其實都只會幫咗蘋果日報增加engagement, 肥佬黎開心都嚟唔切。<br />\n所以你見蘋果日報完全無擔心過, 亦都無處理過比人洗版。<br />\n<br />\n不論藍絲黃絲都有好多人以為比嬲嬲/dislike, comments鬧幾句就可以令對方收皮。其實反而會幫咗人增加engagememt。"},{"pid":"4cc1a02bc5ff8d6db17027d59be22b5056dba293","tid":1481603,"uid":271051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1232aabee54978afb413cffff8133a1ed66be672","tid":1481603,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T18:58:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">make more efficient use of your time</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T21:53:13.000Z","msg":"CANT AGREE MORE"},{"pid":"6b64391f2464a93e77520399f58019c7e31daa9f","tid":1481603,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T23:23:28.000Z","msg":"外文五毛狗點睇，覺得佢哋好易會誤導啲不明白來龍去脈既外國人，又未必真係有咁多留言，又因為冇乜香港人好易畀啲五毛/支那留學生攻佔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d603530414c27c5c7fa2c130e5eefb39a52243ad","tid":1481603,"uid":194553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T23:26:15.000Z","msg":"聽日818遊行一定要Loop聖詩！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1480910\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1480910</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9ec2c94d02643e99fefe0b6ecab50611f3917ab9","tid":1481603,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dis